oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jean Shepard at Hillbilly Heaven Night Club
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Shepard, Jean, 1933-2016; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and blue on white) announcing Grand Ole Opry star Jean Shepard at the Hillbilly Night Club on April 28. Poster features a metal photoplate of Jean Shepard. Poster was printed for job no. 1041. To view the paperwork associated with this order, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/20682.
